text: "Babooshka" is a 1980 song by Kate Bush and is the second single from her third studio album Never for Ever. It went to number 2 in Australia, number 4 in France and Norway, number 5 in Ireland, Israel and the United Kingdom, number 6 in Italy, number 8 in New Zealand, number 12 in South Africa, number 14 in Germany, number 24 in the Netherlands, number 25 in Finland and number 186 in France. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1980 songs Category:Kate Bush songs Category:Art pop songs
